bibliographic-data.invention-title: OPTIMIZING CARBON MONOXIDE PRODUCTION FROMHETEROGENEOUS FEEDSTOCK

abstract.p: It is provided a process for increasing production of carbon monoxide (CO) and recycling carbon dioxide when treating synthesis gas using a carbon dioxide-to-carbon monoxide conversion unit, such as a Reverse Water Gas Shift (RWGS) reactor, converting excess CO2 from the produced syngas to additional CO, using an external source of green, renewable or low carbon intensity hydrogen.
